{"tid":519342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Spotify被音樂出版商告侵權   索償16億美元","createTime":"2018-01-04T09:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T09:36:53.000Z","uid":31314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7649b905f249c9f4a2b587ce019bd7b2e87d2f41","tid":519342,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T09:03:57.000Z","msg":"美國音樂出版商Wixen Music控告音樂串流平台Spotify侵權，指控在無許可或補償給該公司的情況下，使用他們數以千計，甚至是過萬首歌曲，索賠16億美元（約124.8億港元）。該訴訟已在2017年12月29日正式提出。<br />\n<br />\n據外媒報導，<span style=\"color: red;\">Wixen指控Spotify未取得其資料庫中許多歌曲的版權，高達3000首，還詳列了1萬多首有版權疑慮的歌曲，包括傳奇搖滾樂隊The Doors、老牌音樂人Neil Young，以及搖滾巨星Tom Petty的歌曲作品。他們</span>指Spotify在未有取得足夠的正確授權之下，把 Wixen 數千首歌曲在其音樂平台上發佈。<span style=\"color: red;\">Wixen指Spotify只獲得歌曲錄製產品的版權，而並非獲得該歌曲作品的版權</span>，Spotify已成為數十億美元的企業，而歌手與製作人就未能分享到應有的成果。<br />\n<br />\n每首有版權疑慮的歌曲，Wixen Music欲向Spotify索償16萬美元，是美國版權法中最高索償金額。<br />\n<br />\nSpotify拒絕評論此事。Spotify被傳在今年內計劃上市，在過去幾個月公司升值約20%，到至少190億美元（1,482億港元），目前將要面對訴訟，可能會為上市罩上陰霾。"},{"pid":"f2192d70956d8fd5954cedca888b265aa1ebe3c5","tid":519342,"uid":63588,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T09:06:20.000Z","msg":"Spotify 好多歌都無 仲有傻鳩俾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e56a382d3c65724c74a589d63bb2a85f42e34c","tid":519342,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T09:08:08.000Z","msg":"會否拖累騰訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f646a4a61b1863e6e89692249d91a899624ae3","tid":519342,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2e56a382d3c65724c74a589d63bb2a85f42e34c","tid":519342,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T09:08:08.000Z","msg":"會否拖累騰訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T09:12:18.000Z","msg":"700直插<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c62e1313d8908c3f6497ea95cd55a5d75d2b3c","tid":519342,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T09:35:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"379a7adf03cc6ea2f629ce6961ae60ecffa0de03","tid":519342,"uid":22566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T09:36:53.000Z","msg":"16萬定16億呀"}]}